janus.transport.websockets.name: JANUS WebSockets transport plugin
janus.transport.websockets.author: Meetecho s.r.l.
janus.transport.websockets.description: This transport plugin adds WebSockets support to the Janus API via libwebsockets.

janus.plugin.streaming.name: JANUS Streaming plugin
janus.plugin.streaming.author: Meetecho s.r.l.
janus.plugin.streaming.description: This is a streaming plugin for Janus, allowing WebRTC peers to watch/listen to pre-recorded files or media generated by an external source.

janus.plugin.videocall.name: JANUS VideoCall plugin
janus.plugin.videocall.author: Meetecho s.r.l.
janus.plugin.videocall.description: This is a simple video call plugin for Janus, allowing two WebRTC peers to call each other through a server.

janus.plugin.videoroom.name: JANUS VideoRoom plugin
janus.plugin.videoroom.author: Meetecho s.r.l.
janus.plugin.videoroom.description: This is a plugin implementing a videoconferencing SFU (Selective Forwarding Unit) for Janus, that is an audio/video router.

janus.plugin.nosip.name: JANUS NoSIP plugin
janus.plugin.nosip.author: Meetecho s.r.l.
janus.plugin.nosip.description: This is a simple RTP bridging plugin that leaves signalling details (e.g., SIP) up to the application.

janus.plugin.recordplay.name: JANUS Record&Play plugin
janus.plugin.recordplay.author: Meetecho s.r.l.
janus.plugin.recordplay.description: This is a trivial Record&Play plugin for Janus, to record WebRTC sessions and replay them.

janus.plugin.echotest.name: JANUS EchoTest plugin
janus.plugin.echotest.author: Meetecho s.r.l.
janus.plugin.echotest.description: This is a trivial EchoTest plugin for Janus, just used to showcase the plugin interface.
